<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>IELTS Answers</title></head><body><h1>DAILY ROUTINE ANSWERS</h1><h3>Câu 2: What do you usually have for breakfast and how do you cook it?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> How to cook (Fried Egg):<br>I have some eggs for breakfast.<br>I break the egg into the bowl. <br>I put some spices on it. and I mix it.<br>I put the pan into the gas. and heat it.<br>I pour some oil and mixture into the pan.<br>I wait for some minutes. <br>I take it out into the dishes<br>How cook rice.<br>Rice is very easy to cook. <br>I use rice cooker.<br>I wash the rice clearly.<br>then I pour some water, all into the rice cooker.<br>I turn on the cooker and wait 45 minutes.<br>How to cook boil potato.<br>I go to the market to buy some potato.<br>I peal the totato's skin.<br>I wash it clearly.<br>then i prepare a pot.<br>I boil the potato for 30 minutes<br>What is your favourite dishes ?<br>There are many food that i love /favourite dishes.<br>But i really interest in local dishes in my countries.<br>like Banh Trung, Pho, noodle-related dishes. <br>Why do you Pho ? <br>Pho is one of the most famous dish in Viet Nam<br>A lot of people in the world know it. <br>It tastes delicious.<br>How does Pho taste ?<br>The smell is very attractive to me.<br>A little bit sweety, salty.<br>you can add some lemon juice to make it sour (adj): chua<br>or you can add chillisource (tương ớt) to make it spicy (adj): cay.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>culture-related value.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>   </p><hr><h3>Câu 3: Do you like going out for a short walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going out for a short walk?<br>sometimes, i would love to.<br>When and where do you go out for a short walk?.<br>Seldom i go out for a short walk only when i have free time at the weekend. or sometimes i have a day off, i will go out for jogging. <br>Where do you go out for a short walk ?.<br>I go to the small park near my house. It is only a half kilometre. It only takes me five minutes walking.<br>What do you do at the park ?<br>I usually go running and when i feel tired, i will walk slower or seat on the chair under the shadow of the tree. <br>What does the park have, look like ?<br>The park looks small but beautifull.<br>At the park, you can see a small lake, a lot of plants, gardens and flowers neaby. Under the tree, it has many chairs to sit and <br>It has space which has a lot of excercise equipments. You can use it.<br>I can take fresh and cool air.<br>Why do you like going out for a short walk?<br>-> sức khỏe. (it is good for my health) -> It helps me keep fit and charge the energy (B2).<br>-> yên bình (i feel very peacefull and comfortable there)<br>-> you can meet and conmunicate with a lot of people there<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 5: Why do you go for a walk only at the weekend?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Why do you go for a walk only at the weekend?<br>Only at the weekend i have free time.<br>I have go to work on the other days. -> i am with busy with my jobs.<br></p><hr><h3>Câu 6: Do you like going shopping?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going shopping?<br>I'm a shopping lover.<br>but i am careful with my money, so i only buy neccesary goods.<br>Where do you go shopping at ?<br>Before the covid, i used to go to the store to buy directly. <br>But after that, i usually buy online from shoppe app or facebook, ...<br>Do you prefer to shop in person or online ?<br>I like both of them. <br>When i shop in person, i can try on the clothes and i can touch so i can feel the product's quality. and i can ask my friend to go with me and we can talk  and give advices to each other before buying.<br>When i shop online, there are many coupons, i can use it for discounting and i can look for more products and more options to choose. but it has many risks. I can receive falsely advertised products. it does not match me.<br>What do you buy when you go shopping ?<br>I buy a lot. <br>If the price is cheap i will purchase it.<br>i will look for products with deep discount.<br>If my products run out of time i will purchase the new one.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 7: What do you usually buy and where do you go?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you prefer to shop at local market (chợ) or at the supermarket (siêu thị) ?.<br>I usually go to the supermarket because in the suppermarket i can look for the price tags of the products and i do not need to negotiate. It also hass more options to choose from brands, sizes to materials. It has air condition i can feel cooler in the summer, warmer in the winter. <br>What do you not like the local market ?<br>I always have to ask the price of the products. It is inconvinient and uncomfortable. <br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 8: When and Why do you go shopping?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> When and Why do you go shopping?<br>I go shopping when i have something need buying. <br>or at the weekend after i receive my salary. <br>Do you think go shopping is a good hobby (sở thích) ?.<br>I do not think so because if you go shopping too much. I could have to spent too much money on it so you can not save money. <br>It is not good for the environment. many people tend to buy trendy products and give up on old items, it is a waste of merchandises (resources). <br>Why do many people love to buy new clothes ?<br>Because a lot of people follow the fashion trend. <br>Clothes show one's status (position). People can evaluate your value from lookings. <br>Do you think judge other people by there look is good ?<br>It has two sided. On the positive side, the way you wear show a lot about them. If the person who wear tidy and clothes that means the person has good position, they have a lot of money, they are ambitious and careful. Have good lookings is the way to respect your partner.<br>On the negative side, some people who are from poor condition, they do not have money and time but they have a good personality. We should not judge them from their look. <br>"do not judge a book just buy its cover" <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 9: Do you like going out for a drink or eating out?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going out for a drink or eating out?<br>not entirely, sometimes i would love to go out but someitmes i just want to stay at home. It depends on my mood. <br>Where do you go out for a drink ?.<br>I drive my motobike arround Ho Tay lake, and i will stop by nearby caffee shop.<br>What do you like for drink ?.<br>I love a cup of coffee or some juices. (milk-tee, bubble tea, mango, water melon...).<br>Why do you go to the coffee shops ? (part 1).<br>At the shop, it offers free wifi, many options to choose, nice view, <br>It has delicious dessert and drink (đồ ăn tráng miệng)<br>and i can stay there for a long time to talk with other people or do my work.<br>Do you prefer to go alone or with your friends ?<br>It depends on my mood, sometimes when i feel sad i just want to be alone but sometimes when i feel excited and happy i want to spend time with my friends. We stay at the coffee shop, and talk for hours.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> <br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 10: Where and When do you usually meet your friends?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> What do you talk about ?<br>We talk about works and personal lifes. <br>Sometimes, when i get into troubles, i need advices from my friends.<br>Do you prefer eating out ?<br>not entirely, i want to control food's origin and quality.<br>Do you love cookings ?<br>I hate food's smell when i cook but to meet up my casual life i have to cook for myself but i cook the basic dishes only.<br>Why do many people love cooking ?<br>I think they want to cook what they want. It is one of the good hobby. If you can garantee the food's quality and origin. Some peopel are good at cooking so they want to show their talents to other people.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br>   </p><hr><h3>Câu 12: Do you like watching TV or going to the gym?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like watching TV ?.<br>Before having the mobile phone, i usually watched TV but now i watch my mobile phone instead. <br>What do you watch on TV ?.<br>I usually watch films, advertisements, gameshows, music, animal life, ...<br>What is your favourite show ?<br>My favourite show is "who will be the billions"<br>When does the show start ? at 8 pm a day a week but i do not remember exact number.<br>What is the show about ?<br>It is a gameshow, it has two characters, a MC and a player (guest). MC will ask the guest 12 questions and if the player answer correctly. The player will receive the bonus. The more correct questions, the higher bonus. The questions relate to lifes, cultures, foods, awards, .... It is highly various. It require wide knowledge about many fields. <br><br>  <br>  <br><br><br> <br><br><br> <br><br><br><br></p><hr></body></html>